{"tid":2366784,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"張艾嘉鄭欣宜洪永城等藝人合作拍攝短片 攜手支持「可重用口罩運動」","createTime":"2021-01-14T21:33:40.000Z","updateTime":"2021-01-15T08:36:59.000Z","uid":130626,"like":0,"dislike":46,"uniUserReply":16,"replies":[{"pid":"70c9d735c1ad7e1059afe03c2692d6c6d0a74353","tid":2366784,"uid":130626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-14T21:33:40.000Z","msg":"由於疫情肆虐，即棄口罩成為普羅大眾外出的必需品。可是，即棄口罩的物料很難進行回收，並且需要很多年才能分解，造成嚴重環境問題。有見及此，非牟利環保團體與服裝品牌D舉辦「可重用口罩運動」，旨在鼓勵市民在適當的場合下，可以選擇使用可重用口罩，保護環境。<br />\n<br />\n今次的活動邀請了20位來自不同界別的人士參與，各位藝人、環保人士、醫生、運動員一起拍攝宣傳影片。參與人士包括︰藝人張艾嘉、林德信、鄭欣宜、倪晨曦、林恬兒、汪詩詩、丁子高、洪永城、香港政府食物及衞生局前局長周一嶽等，影片中的旁白由鄭啟泰聲演。<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.nextmgz.com/webarticle/2_773257_0/%E5%BC%B5%E8%89%BE%E5%98%89%E9%84%AD%E6%AC%A3%E5%AE%9C%E6%B4%AA%E6%B0%B8%E5%9F%8E%E7%AD%89%E8%97%9D%E4%BA%BA%E5%90%88%E4%BD%9C%E6%8B%8D%E6%94%9D%E7%9F%AD%E7%89%87-%E6%94%9C%E6%89%8B%E6%94%AF%E6%8C%81-%E5%8F%AF%E9%87%8D%E7%94%A8%E5%8F%A3%E7%BD%A9%E9%81%8B%E5%8B%95-\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.nextmgz.com%2Fwebarticle%2F2_773257_0%2F%25E5%25BC%25B5%25E8%2589%25BE%25E5%2598%2589%25E9%2584%25AD%25E6%25AC%25A3%25E5%25AE%259C%25E6%25B4%25AA%25E6%25B0%25B8%25E5%259F%258E%25E7%25AD%2589%25E8%2597%259D%25E4%25BA%25BA%25E5%2590%2588%25E4%25BD%259C%25E6%258B%258D%25E6%2594%259D%25E7%259F%25AD%25E7%2589%2587-%25E6%2594%259C%25E6%2589%258B%25E6%2594%25AF%25E6%258C%2581-%25E5%258F%25AF%25E9%2587%258D%25E7%2594%25A8%25E5%258F%25A3%25E7%25BD%25A9%25E9%2581%258B%25E5%258B%2595-&d=qXcR1A%2FTALq%2FhnoNE0cJVcyZng7V5AOcQmv89xdKlzQ%3D&h=d251b280\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.nextmgz.com%2Fwebarticle%2F2_773257_0%2F%25E5%25BC%25B5%25E8%2589%25BE%25E5%2598%2589%25E9%2584%25AD%25E6%25AC%25A3%25E5%25AE%259C%25E6%25B4%25AA%25E6%25B0%25B8%25E5%259F%258E%25E7%25AD%2589%25E8%2597%259D%25E4%25BA%25BA%25E5%2590%2588%25E4%25BD%259C%25E6%258B%258D%25E6%2594%259D%25E7%259F%25AD%25E7%2589%2587-%25E6%2594%259C%25E6%2589%258B%25E6%2594%25AF%25E